						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1392 (1470 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. Seems to record the gift of a village as <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> by a <hi rend="italic">mahāsāmanta</hi> (name lost) to the deity on the occasion of an eclipse. The details of the date are lost, except for the <hi rend="bold">Śaka year 1392</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1470 A.D.</hi></p>						

